04:14.000 --> 04:16.000
But for every one of these comics,

04:16.000 --> 04:18.000
there were dozens of poor imitators

04:18.000 --> 04:20.000
out to replicate their popularity and profit

04:20.000 --> 04:22.000
by reusing the same tropes.

04:22.000 --> 04:25.000
An explosion in the gaming webcomic had begun,

04:25.000 --> 04:27.000
and it would continue for over a decade.

04:27.000 --> 04:30.000
